name: Google I/O Extended Bizerte 2018
description:
Google I/O is an annual event hosted by Google to highlight the latest in technology and product innovation. This covers topics such as the IoT, working with material design, advancements in mobile technology, Machine Learning and so much more.

I/O Extended 2018 is an event that aims to put together the developers community in Bizerte to discuss and learn about the new technologies introduced at Google I/O 2018.

We invite you to join GDG Bizerte a cozy and warm atmosphere at "Maison des jeunes Mateur" to experience the magic and innovation of Google I/O

Agende :
-Google I/O Recap: New Google products & technology Announcements
- CodeLab Session in Flutter Framework
- Open Talk with GDG Members

and a lot of Gifts & fun Don't miss the date ;)
